            "created_at": "2017-12-16T22:23:24Z",
            "updated_at": "2017-12-16T22:23:24Z",
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "If found that when using: \r\n\r\n```\r\n@app.template_filter()\r\ndef foo(bar):\r\n    pass\r\n```\r\nSomewhere in my main code.\r\nI still need:\r\n```\r\nif __name__ == '__main__':\r\n    app.jinja_env.auto_reload = True\r\n    app.run(debug=True, host='0.0.0.0')\r\n```\r\n\r\nTo make template reloading on page refresh work. I didn't need `app.config['TEMPLATES_AUTO_RELOAD'] = True`."
        },
